Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝乃冒險者嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠潛過名為"危險"之瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探求位於其深處的\N傳說真相之人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是,就來將吾尋得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時值西元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接連發生離奇的船難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們謠傳此為自古便棲息於\N海底的怪獸所為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各國首腦則認為此為\N新武器之攻擊而彼此責難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊張的氣氛不斷升溫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此同時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自工業革命後\N工業與科學迅速發展
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:01:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各強國為了爭奪\N亞洲、非洲殖民地而彼此對立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍事衝突一再上演
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19世紀末
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有志之士們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都籠罩在一觸即發的\N世界大戰陰影之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在你眼前  有著無限的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底兩萬哩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭懦弱的人  無法背叛藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作夢之前  我想翱翔天際
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的音樂盒開啟  發出聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點一滴演奏出幸福與勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在你眼前  有著無限的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言語是永遠的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  forget  to  try  in  mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛比寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴黎…巴黎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾菲爾鐵塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#01  艾菲爾鐵塔的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是巴黎萬國博覽會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要再等一個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要推擠,請不要推擠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,光這樣還是飛不上天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,驅動系統顯得太累贅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得自己好像是來看人\N而不是來看發明的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在宣佈第一屆國際飛行比賽\N正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項競賽內容為\N飛行距離愈遠者獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優勝者可獲得2萬法郎獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑丈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,我在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉,我來晚了\N-是嗎,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,1號機快要掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,你看那傢伙如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的機翼\N根本撐不住引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風力2啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是順風\N但能飛個8公尺就不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀錄為8公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-果然\N-果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是2號機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地越過多佛海峽\N從英國遠道而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克萊特爵爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活該,笨貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑丈,我們是幾號?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抽到102號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要等到傍晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然早了點\N先把機體從船上卸下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坐船過來時有沒有暈船啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,一路都很舒適
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在船上完成這麼多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,真抱歉\N都怪我不能搭船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一說到船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說美國派出了新戰艦\N要去對付海底的怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以為你爸報仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不確定他已經過世了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22號機,皮耶號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優勝呼聲很高喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這情況來看\N優勝是我們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該會獲得\N壓倒性的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子2萬法郎的獎金\N也是我們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天起可以肆無忌憚地\N盡情發明了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下我老婆可沒話說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先好好玩遍巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你一心想找到你爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,你也該找個女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧,強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,把那邊的扳手拿給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑丈,我先離開一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2萬法郎呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚我一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2萬法郎耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了,就是那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個\N可千萬別讓她給逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她的目的地應該是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾菲爾鐵塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法國?西班牙?義大利\N埃及?非洲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王\N我到底來自哪個國家呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會跟你一樣都是非洲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算問你你也不會知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能飛的話\N或許就能去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以飛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強·洛克·拉帝格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是能帶妳飛上天的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不信嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的飛得起來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是為了參加那場飛行大賽\N而從勒阿弗爾來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是從哪裡來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等,我來猜猜看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是印度對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?錯了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我並不認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,妳終於開口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在擔心跟妳語言會不通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,我並不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也覺得我的膚色很罕見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就難說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有何貴幹?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦,我想說難得來巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟妳交個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的貓喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠是獅子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情別那麼陰沉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生只有一次,開心享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心享受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?\N好厲害的發明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當眾談情說愛\N好歹也要有點分寸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才一直看著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒完沒了,沒完沒了…\N-大姊頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別遷怒到小孩子身上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對,還是快點進入正題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖把妳胸前的\N玻璃墜子交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋找擁有這東西的妳\N我們可是跑遍了整個歐洲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不然…\N-不然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小孩子這樣做\N實在太丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-桑森\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韓森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-別跑!\N-別跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓她給跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了\N我曉得那女孩會去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊頭,是哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她的身手加上那隻怪貓\N當然就是那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著還沒有人來\N我們快下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕盈的身手加上怪貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了,是馬戲團
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔,這個女孩的表演何時開始?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,原來她平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演的時間到了\N快換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團長,今天我不想上台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得會發生什麼不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天妳有吃早餐對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就該付出同等的勞力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位來賓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就來介紹她出場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叢林舞姬,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:14:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來她叫娜蒂亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以擺出一副\N凶神惡煞的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可要合法地\N與對方溝通喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,使用偽幣算合法嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太多話了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事想跟你談談
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多麥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薛提,奈費特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位給予熱烈的掌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是娜蒂亞公主的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bonjour,  Mademoiselle.\N(小姐您好)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了,她不是妳的姊姊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,我叫葛蘭迪絲·格蘭帕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找妳,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟姊姊一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子還是送花好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣掙扎個不停\N吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起\N我就是妳的監護人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還付了錢\N謝謝人家對妳至今的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給她三分顏色\N她倒開起染坊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不白費唇舌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我抓回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-遵命\N-遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞,聽我說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那3個人要抓妳對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就坐這個一起逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以靠自己擺脫他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我名字\N好像我們很熟似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是馬戲團演員了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼逞強嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙\N為什麼要搶這顆石頭?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西那麼珍貴嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不想說就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用跑的是追不上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害,是鐵製的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰發明的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想嚐苦頭的話就過來這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:17:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好讓你們明白\N瞧不起大人會有什麼下場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種玩具怎麼可能逃得掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要動手了,大姊頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,放手去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-韓森\N-我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們別這樣啦,很危險耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼,不可以妨礙大人辦事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去反省一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著還沒有人來礙事\N快用飛行模式開溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危險,我還以為死定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纏人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼處理?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨他去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正"蔚藍之水"\N已經在我們手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!  Adios!\N(再見)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再見\N-再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強那小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑丈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你好久了,強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能飛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再快一點嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣已經是最快了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還不如在地上跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到99號機,日之本號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-居然有人突然插隊?\N-抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往上飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接飛越多佛海峽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會了,心愛的花都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳等著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-娜蒂亞,妳沒事吧?\N-我掙脫不開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用紙做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點制住這隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠是獅子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊頭,我可不想年紀輕輕\N就墜機死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心,下面是塞納河
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個孩子還蠻有本事的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我絕對不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會放棄蔚藍之水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走水路他們就追不上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:21:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就開這艘船逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會冷?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會,你叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?我沒說過嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過份喔\N強,我叫強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳接下來有什麼打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回馬戲團嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳的家人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,那就跟我一樣囉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.57,0:22:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就到勒阿弗爾來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:22:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姑丈家也在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑丈跟姑姑都是很熱心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會願意幫妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.01,0:23:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑丈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,強\N是特別獎喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,因為是臨時獎項\N所以沒有獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好幹喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待續)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:24:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼應付心中的焦急才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要看不清遠方的夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喃喃自語  仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你的約定耀眼閃爍著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try  安慰的話語\N是傳達不到內心的風
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.60,0:24:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然背負的不安逐漸膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.31,0:24:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我自己的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.61,0:24:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人應該也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.28,0:24:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使跌倒或感到迷惘\N仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.43,0:25:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞,這就是我的研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.30,0:25:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全都是你做的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.44,0:25:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會開我發明的飛機\N送妳回故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.78,0:25:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.51,0:25:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖交出蔚藍之水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.28,0:25:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好煩人的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.78,0:25:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姊姊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.25,0:25:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底兩萬哩  下一回\N「小小逃亡者」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.25,0:25:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要看喔\N-要看喔
